      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "If you’re afraid the app will grow stale as you keep getting the same questions, the museum has already thought about that very thing. Museum Educator Deb Howard has plans to keep updating the pool of questions regularly, keeping the game fresh and exciting for all who play.",
