          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "For those who want to bone up further on their Corvette trivia skills, they can check out the Vetteacademy videos available on the museum’s YouTube channel. Many of the questions for the app come from the videos, plus it’s an entertaining way to study more about the iconic car.",
